\end_layout

\end_inset

: AUC is closely related to the 
\color red
Mann-Whitney U test
\color inherit
, which tests whether positives are ranked higher than negatives.
 It is also equivalent to the 
\color red
Wilcoxon test of ranks
\color inherit
.
\end_layout

