\begin_layout Standard
We refer to 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{i1}$
\end_inset

's as the 
\shape italic
scores
\shape default
 of the first principal component.
 It happens so that each element in 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{1}$
\end_inset

